The Rubric

All homework will turned in by publishing a Quarto document to your GitHub account. See either the online GitHub Pages Documentation or the module in your course that covered GitHub integration for how to do this. The following rubric will be used in the course CANVAS site (denoted as Online Homework Rubric there) to evaluate the scores of each homework assignment using the following general criteria. Since this rubric applies to a series of homework assignents, you should quickly become familiar with the requirements to gain full marks.
